<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    
    <!-- 

        This file contains the HTML and embedded JavaScript (EJS) template for the "Edit Product" page in the admin section of the web shop.

        Structure:
        - A container div that holds the entire form.
        - A row div that contains the header and the form.
        - A header section with a title "Edit Product".
        - A form section inside a styled container for editing product details.

        Form Details:
        - The form uses the POST method to submit data to the "/edit-product" endpoint.
        - It includes a hidden input field for the product ID.
        - It has input fields for the product title, description, price, and image URL.
        - Each input field is pre-filled with the current product details using EJS syntax.
        - The form includes a submit button labeled "Update Product".

        Note:
        - The image input field has a placeholder text in Estonian: "Palun sisesta LINK!" which translates to "Please enter LINK!".
    -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h1 class="text-center">Edit Product</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12">

                <div class="product-add-container p-2 bg-dark rounded text-white">
                    <form action="/edit-product" method="POST">
                        <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= product.id %>">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="title" class="form-label">Title</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title" name="title" value="<%= product.title %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="description" class="form-label">Description</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="description" name="description"><%= product.description %></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="price" class="form-label">Price</label>
                            <input type="number" class="form-control" id="price" name="price" value="<%= product.price %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="image" class="form-label">Image</label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="Palun sisesta LINK!" class="form-control" id="image" name="image">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success p-2">Update Product</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>